div.b:
Prepare POST payload
to send to news server
div.p:
The data always contains 2 instance hashes, database UID, iTop
environment, (iTop) application name and version, encryption library to
use, API version (in order to retrieve a response in this format)
div.div:
News source implementations may add additional data here.
Final payload contains operation, API version
and a base64 encoded version of the data above.
